00:12:00.600 --> 00:12:01.900
if you don't remember them all.

00:12:01.900 --> 00:12:03.200
You know, maybe you'll
have mnemonic device to --

00:12:03.200 --> 00:12:04.500
&gt;&gt; Jonathan Haidt: Okay.

00:12:04.500 --> 00:12:05.800
&gt;&gt; John Haskell: But, so, why --

00:12:05.800 --> 00:12:07.100
what's this dividing
line about in 2014?

00:12:07.100 --> 00:12:08.420
Why is it 2014?

00:12:08.420 --> 00:12:10.040
Was it something in 2014?

