00:37:23.360 --> 00:37:25.220
universities need to --

00:37:25.220 --> 00:37:28.480
we're going to punish those that
don't have 50% Conservatives.

00:37:28.480 --> 00:37:29.780
I mean, this is not helpful.

00:37:29.780 --> 00:37:31.080
This is not a good idea.

00:37:31.080 --> 00:37:33.270
So, I think that
we can solve it.

00:37:33.270 --> 00:37:35.070
I think we now have the will.

00:37:35.070 --> 00:37:36.900
We now have a much
