00:37:58.850 --> 00:38:00.150
That's the nature

00:38:00.150 --> 00:38:02.490
of a polarization cycle
and a culture war.

00:38:02.490 --> 00:38:04.830
So, I'd really rather
they just stay out of it.

00:38:04.830 --> 00:38:06.980
&gt;&gt; John Haskell: But it
